lead_paragraph: Democratic U.S. presidential candidate Hillary Clinton called the shooting in Orlando, Florida, "an act of terror" that requires the nation to "redouble" efforts to stop similar attacks.

headline.main: Democrat Hillary Clinton Calls Orlando Shooting 'an Act of Terror'
